replies.body:
Man, follow your dreams. Even minor streamers make a decent amount of cash, and if you have the charisma you can easily make a career out of it.
Think about the movie Finding Nemo. If Marlin never went on his epic journey, he would have never learnt about what truly makes him an excellent fish/father. Go for it, you are at a point in your life where if you don't make a leap you could fall into a puddle of stagnation. And stagnation is not conductive for a healthy and **happy** life. 

So go my friend, and follow your dream. MAKE THIS A REALITY WITH YOUR OWN TWO HANDS! strive for _**magis**_, **i know you can do it** ;) {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
